# Constraints

Follow [`docs/CONSTRAINTS.md`](docs/CONSTRAINTS.md) on every task.

- Touch only what the user asked for; no drive-by changes.
- Never act outside this repository unless the user explicitly directs a path **and** confirms after you restate it.
- Keep secrets in `.env`; never expose the private inquire email in the UI.
